      <title>澳大利亚财务主管说，特朗普金属关税是自我破坏的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/australia-deserves-better-from-the-us-on-tariffs-treasurer-chalmers-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财务主管吉姆·查尔默斯（Jim Chalmers）表示，美国对钢铁和铝的关税是“自欺欺人的”，澳大利亚值得更好的待遇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/australia-deserves-better-from-the-us-on-tariffs-treasurer-chalmers-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:16:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战改道的交付，中国停止了液化天然气进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/china-halts-us-lng-imports-as-trade-war-reroutes-deliveries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已经40天从美国进口了液化天然气，这是近两年来最长的差距，因为交易员被迫将货物转移到其他地方，以避免北京对超冷燃料的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/china-halts-us-lng-imports-as-trade-war-reroutes-deliveries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普律师在委内瑞拉驱逐出境数据上使法官处于黑暗之中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-lawyers-keep-judge-in-dark-on-venezuelan-deportation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府律师挑衅地辩护唐纳德·特朗普总统驱逐了数百名涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员，并拒绝向法官提供信息，他说他需要确定政府是否忽略了他的命令，以将飞机转回美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-lawyers-keep-judge-in-dark-on-venezuelan-deportation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 23:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他正在授权政府生产煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-he-s-authorizing-administration-to-produce-coal-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他希望通过授权他的政府从化石燃料中增加能源的产量来应对中国的经济优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-he-s-authorizing-administration-to-produce-coal-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 23:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普谈论分裂资产提示在与普京的电话会议之前关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-talk-of-dividing-assets-prompts-concern-before-his-call-with-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美国和俄罗斯已经在谈论将“资产”分配为结束乌克兰战斗的一部分，这是他可能准备牺牲基夫在周二与弗拉基米尔·普京说话时牺牲利益的最新信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-talk-of-dividing-assets-prompts-concern-before-his-call-with-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 23:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《外星敌人法》是什么？特朗普为什么要用它来驱逐委内瑞拉？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/alien-enemies-act-how-trump-used-the-law-to-deport-venezuelans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普总统于3月14日下令驱逐数百名涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员时，他援引了自第二次世界大战以来就没有使用过的有争议的美国法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/alien-enemies-act-how-trump-used-the-law-to-deport-venezuelans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 22:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普目标是在最新的大门举动中进行工会谈判的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-targets-spending-on-labor-union-talks-in-latest-doge-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府要求联邦机构报告他们在过去一年中花费了多少谈判工会合同，这表明集体谈判协议可能是政府削减成本推动力的下一个目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-targets-spending-on-labor-union-talks-in-latest-doge-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 22:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉承诺将被驱逐到萨尔瓦多监狱的人释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuela-pledges-to-free-citizens-deported-to-el-salvador-jail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国民议会领袖豪尔赫·罗德里格斯（JorgeRodríguez）称，委内瑞拉将做“任何事情”，以使数百名被美国驱逐出萨尔瓦多臭名昭著的监狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuela-pledges-to-free-citizens-deported-to-el-salvador-jail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 18:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
